{"tid":2458640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺女朋友背後同同事曖昧","createTime":"2021-03-23T14:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T15:09:32.000Z","uid":86743,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dcdea648572ba6843530c52dbbb3d6586e4d1b1b","tid":2458640,"uid":86743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"我有個一齊左好幾年嘅女朋友，感情一直都好好，不過因為各有各工作，所以一個星期先見1-2日。呢排反工有位女同事對自己好好，感覺佢都係自己鐘意嗰type。其實佢都有男朋友，但係佢同我唔知點解對對方嘅私下故事都好感興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身我地無咩嘅，但係佢間唔中拎對波撞我手臂，又行得我好近。最近傾起按摩，佢仲無啦啦幫我按，真係好曖昧。<br />\n<br />\n有時我想同佢拉遠反啲距離，但係我個心其實係enjoy，唸起都覺得變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d61ffa6771d44de34eeebde0d48ac6ff1745fa","tid":2458640,"uid":135137,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:38:51.000Z","msg":"係到食係到柯唔會有好收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ef7dee82d908f3ea0417c2fe2f179a088708e0","tid":2458640,"uid":44807,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"識得返屋企就得"},{"pid":"7d91866897cba8e2f86f0d58a5ff47ce934643b2","tid":2458640,"uid":65297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"你好變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68bf84b7aa3ddfbf7cba46ccb679d36808cae4a","tid":2458640,"uid":255106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"食左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食完你先有故事"},{"pid":"a1b6c227478b9a30e433c792cd66453c4784cc02","tid":2458640,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"一星期見一兩日唔係好正常咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e627580ce96ddb82a2eab4f6c79116f3efdb862","tid":2458640,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021